Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hinazuki is late?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She said she was going to\Ngive me my present today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she was up all night\Nmaking something,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it makes sense that she'd be late...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}HOPE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ice Hockey Club\N1988 National Champions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rubber boots?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An adult male's size...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It snowed the night before last.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, an adult male\Ncame here after that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Five court musicians\Nplaying drums and fifes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fun Girls' Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.95,0:01:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}THURSDAY, MARCH 3rd, 1988\NKAYO HINAZUKI DISAPPEARED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:03:00.25,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERASED
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, I stayed home\Nfrom school for two days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is Mom out shopping?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, a similar incident\Nhappened in a neighboring city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They caught the culprit\Nsoon afterwards, but now this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know who did it yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we'd better do everything in our power\Nto prevent it from happening again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course that's part of it,\Nbut about clamping down on the press...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you right after\NI talk to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll talk to city hall, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom's former co-worker...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A reporter for TV Ishikari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The kids shouldn't have to\Nremember something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is where it started...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.10,SignNC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HOKU-HOKU BENTO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not your fault, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want Hinazuki to be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There must have been something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking it's your fault\Nafter the fact is just pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's only so much one person can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That holds true for me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being alone here\Nonly makes you depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's eat before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been keeping something from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I lied when I said\NKayo was at home with a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She moved to her grandmother's\Nhome for personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It happened so suddenly that she wasn't\Nable to say goodbye to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I hear Kayo is doing well in Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ran away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard her mother beat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You'll see her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The school and the PTA had a discussion\Nand decided what to say about Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,\Ngo along with this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems the press has been muzzled,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but a police vehicle has been parked{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}near Hinazuki's house\Nfor the past several days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently her mother\Nis a suspect at this stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only six days after Hinazuki disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}LOOKING FOR
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}AYA NAKANISHI\N11 YEARS OLD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 8th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 9th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The city has issued an advisory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you leave school grounds,\Nalways be with a guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}A second child has disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}It's sooner than I expected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 9th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 10th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru... have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About Aya Nakanishi\Nfrom Izumi Elementary?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine from Izumi Elementary\Nsaid she ran away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then went to live\Nwith her grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds just like Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the part\Nabout running away is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is really a case of serial abductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 10th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 11th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are differences in details,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but we've definitely begun to go down\Nthe same flow of time as 18 years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 11th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 12th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}KAYO HINAZUKI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}NEXT UP:\NELEMENTARY SCHOOL STUDENT MISSING\NHOKKAIDO - CHILDREN'S WHEREABOUTS UNKNOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}The investigation became public,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}but TV Ishikari only ran news of the story\Nearly in the morning and late at night,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}and adults with children were advised\Nto only let them watch TV Ishikari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 12th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}March 13th 1988
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The police car that had been camping out\Nin front of Hinazuki's house day and night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}only appeared sporadically\Nafter the Aya Nakanishi disappearance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The focus of the investigation\Nmust have shifted to "serial abductions."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just ten days after her\Ndaughter disappeared...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inside the garbage bag she threw out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were a pair of knit mittens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll give you your present tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a promise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where am I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I back?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In 2006...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23-1, 4th Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The victim is Sachiko Fujinuma,\N52 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're searching for Satoru Fujinuma,\N29 years old, as a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We do have eyewitness\Ninformation. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Are you Satoru Fujinuma?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wrong. You're wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't help Hinazuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom is still murdered...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I'm the suspect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the reality I'm faced with.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get ready!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Episode 5\NGetaway
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, I'm under a bridge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Some imagination I've got...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I haven't\Nmade the news yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First off, I have to think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why was Mom murdered?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because she realized\Nthe identity of the culprit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was her cell phone in the apartment?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What about her bag?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, neither were there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the killer took them away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because it was possible\NMom would've leaked info about him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My head feels heavy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to sleep the day away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time you were absent\Nfrom work without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri was worried about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, I'm sure\Nthere's a reasonable explanation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's eat up first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you had a fight\Nwith your mother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Old people can be set in their ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay here as long as you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you've gotta patch\Nthings up with your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want a beer too, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My impression was right.\NHe is the "annoying big brother" type.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry for lying to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}The police received a tip\Nand hurried over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}They discovered the body of a woman{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}believed to be the mother\Nof the apartment's resident.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}The police are currently\Nsearching for the male resident{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}as a person of interest in the case.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This has taken a disastrous turn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}And now, sports.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Today the Japanese soccer team\Nleft for Germany,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}where the playoffs will be held.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been way too naïve!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No. I can't blame the manager!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's always trying to do the right thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course he'd give me up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Son of a bitch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You called me "Airi," Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't leave your phone on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll track you with GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hop on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to get away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Katagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Airi."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Riding double on the bike\Nmakes us equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind letting me in your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do know what happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The police came to the shop today\Nand talked to the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was on the news, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you killed\Nyour mom, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they're chasing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the one who's grieving the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though you really are connected\Nto a lot of crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}NIPPON\NSHOWA'S MOST SHOCKING CRIMES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot it at the shop the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I read the part you had bookmarked\Nwith an envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It happened in your hometown\Nwhen you were a kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo Hinazuki's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To die on the day of the Girls' Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cried when I read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Girls' Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. March 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can relax here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take the bike back to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about leaving this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.70,BigSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO HINAZUKI\N(10 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The book's information has changed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:47.02,BigSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO HINAZUKI\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then... it can be changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can go back there one more time,\NI can save Hinazuki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. I'm in Airi's room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear Satoru,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it would be a good idea\Nif I went about my normal routine today,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I'm going to work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My family will probably\Nleave the house around ten.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They said they'll be back\Nafter eight tonight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The house key and bike key\Nare next to the clock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My cell phone number is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:29.02,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SASAOKA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not "Katagiri."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Mr. Nishizono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your father's debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My dad was overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said one stoplight\Nand one pedestrian crossing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,totally changed the flow\Nof customers for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That has more to do with your\Nfather's business acumen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was give him a little boost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's a school route.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We would occasionally talk\Nabout it at city council meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Manager! I just finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take-out pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can treat you once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is for my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A girl, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, she's only 17,\Nand still immature...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I should be on my way as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}CHINESE CAFETERIA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part of the sales promotion, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also... about Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that he murdered his...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that he did any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you happen to run into him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do what you can to help him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're all on the same side,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so contact me too if you see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I close in on the killer\Nby investigating like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A child abduction\Nin the city three years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, I recall that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The suspect was arrested\Nthree weeks later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he claimed he was innocent\Nthe whole time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something bothers me about this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want with the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to help Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said we were all on the same side!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You have the wrong idea, Airi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, um, was worried about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you\Ntell me that from the start?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to trust you, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manager... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,don't call the police over to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me a chance to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go back to that house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it's not really\Nyour parents' house, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's big brother\Nand his wife live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My parents live out in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to find a boarding house\Nso I could commute to high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but they invited me\Nto stay with them in Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one more question?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airi, how can you believe in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that I "can."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was still in elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my dad and I went grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A chocolate bar fell out of his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a small town\Nand we knew the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he admitted to stealing it\Nand apologized,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the owner said he would\Nlet the matter drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Dad refused to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was a kind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time I heard him yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The owner felt obliged to call the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Dad, a member\Nof the local agricultural coop,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was suspended for three\Nmonths as punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know! I saw the whole thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You didn't do anything, Dad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad quit the coop,\Ngot a divorce, and left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Mom thought\Nhe really did steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe you for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the flip side to someone\Nsaying "please believe me."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the police I threatened you,\Nforcing you to hide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can get away\Nby yourself, and I refuse to tell them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you stop asking me if I'm stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll at least bring you\Na change of clothes, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Manager...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, he didn't make\Na report to the police.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Incoming Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.73,Grab,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sachiko Fujinuma's Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}This is Satoru Fujinuma.\NStay right where you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru found his mom's phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's from the killer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Stay right where you are"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-You've gotta be kidding me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
